---
title: German Chicken with Creamy Dijon Sauce  plus Rosemary Potatoes & Roasted Carrots
description: Get ready for a hearty dinner inspired by our friends at HelloFresh Germany! You’ll elevate seared pork filets with a velvety Dijon cream sauce that cascades luxuriously over every bite. Serve with golden brown roasted rosemary potatoes and carrots, and sprinkle with herbaceous parsley for a meal that’s fit for weeknights and special occasions too.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66eaf8e28e45e3ca00862a7e-42f9cf07.jpeg
